aid you nearly fifty billion dollars,"],[3465,3549,"didn't she?"],[3570,3741,"We have all the proof."],[3816,4062,"Financial records, offshore transfers."],[4091,4283,"You're not just fired."],[4366,4592,"You'll also be facing fraud charges."],[4629,4771,"I hope you like prisons."],[4800,4904,"You'll be staying there"],[4904,5005,"a very long time."],[5030,5092,"Wait."],[5209,5284,"What about our"],[5284,5380,"ten-billion-dollar deal?"],[5480,5572,"What do you think?"],[5647,5768,"Of course it's void."],[5918,6076,"I told you, Ethan."],[6243,6631,"Everything that you have, I gave it to you."],[6694,6748,"No."],[6777,6869,"This isn't happening."],[6869,7048,"You are not Ms. Carrington."],[7102,7244,"Your last name might be Carrington,"],[7265,7394,"but she's my ex-wife."],[7419,7632,"We were married for seven years."],[7720,7857,"She was just locked in jail"],[7857,7957,"just last week."],[7974,8195,"And now, she's the heiress"],[8195,8425,"of the richest family in the country?"],[8508,8658,"This is all a scam!"]],"28":[[70,221,"You are not fooling us"],[221,329,"with this nonsense."],[329,554,"She is nothing but a fraud."],[554,696,"Fresh out of prison."],[725,884,"And she's trying to sleep her"],[884,1009,"way to the top."],[1009,1280,"You fucking little slut."],[1280,1388,"There is no way"],[1388,1530,"you are Ms. Carrington."],[1530,1689,"But the security team did say"],[1689,1768,"they only answer"],[1768,1922,"to the Carrington heiress."],[2052,2268,"That's because my dear ex-wife here"],[2268,2385,"cheated on me"],[2385,2673,"and spread her legs to Mr. Hawthorne."],[2706,2927,"They have been working together"],[2927,3165,"to ruin my deal with the Carringtons."],[3165,3219,"Oh."],[3286,3440,"So that's what this is about."],[3545,3636,"What now, Nicole?"],[3766,3995,"Just admit that you did all of this"],[4079,4204,"to get me back."],[4250,4471,"And I might forgive you."],[5025,5234,"You filthy bastard."],[6285,6381,"Mr. Carrington."],[6564,6856,"How dare you in